T02TD1528E:85b-0: @85b // dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma lta sgom spyod gsum gyi brda bstan te /
T02TD1528E:86a-0: padma seng ge glang chen gsum spyod pa'i brda ri dags shel dang @86a * //
T02TD1528E:86a-1: nyi ma gsum sgom pa'i brda chu bo me dang rin chen gsum lta ba'i brda'o //
T02TD1528E:86a-2: rdo rje mkha' 'gro mas ro snyoms rnam pa gsum bstan pa //
T02TD1528E:86a-3: sha za smyon pa ce spyang gsum lus kyi ro snyoms ro langs sa ra sa bu chung gsum brtul zhugs kyi ro snyoms nam mkha' sprin dang glog gsum ting nge 'dzin gyi ro snyoms so //
T02TD1528E:86a-4: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma thabs dang shes rab gnyis med zung 'jug gsum gyi brda'o //
T02TD1528E:86a-5: btsun mo bran dang rta mchog gsum shes rab kyi brda'o //
T02TD1528E:86a-6: gcer bu gling pa lam chen gsum thabs shes rab zung 'jug pa'i brda'o //
T02TD1528E:86a-8: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa la rang bzhin chos nyid glong du gnas pa /
T02TD1528E:86a-11: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa /
T02TD1528E:86a-12: ngo bo spros pa dang bral ba /
T02TD1528E:86a-13: skye med yin pas btsal du med pa'o //
T02TD1528E:86a-14: rdo rje'i tshig rkang yin no rdzogs so /
